name: Santa Rosa
description: The Santa Rosa LED series lantern captures the look and feel of the Old West with turn-of-the-century styling. It bridges the era of the gas lamp into a new generation of style and sophistication, providing smooth, diffused illumination for safety and a beautiful lighting ambiance. The Santa Rosa LED is a one of the kind fixture with over 100 lumens per watt and is on the DLC QPL.
